<p>The <code>@parameter:name</code> property returns a specific named parameter value.</p>

<h2>Access Named Parameters</h2>
<pre>{open}users sort="name" limit="3"{close}
  Sort: {open}@parameter:sort{close}, Limit: {open}@parameter:limit{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
{users sort="name" limit="3"}
  {@first}
    Sort: {@parameter:sort}, Limit: {@parameter:limit}
  {/@first}
{/users}

<h2>Note</h2>
<p>Use <code>@parameter:paramName</code> to access specific named parameters passed to the tag. Returns NULL if the parameter doesn't exist.</p>
